        <updated>2025-01-23T18:37:11.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="alttabwindowdelayer">Alt tab window delayer</h1>
<p>This mod improves the Alt+Tab behavior by introducing a short delay before
displaying the tasks window. It helps reduce visual distractions by preventing
brief flickers when quickly switching between apps, similar to how macOS and
Ubuntu handle fast app switching.</p>]]></content>
